Quickstrike:






Staring nervously at the gather of bots, Quickstrike slowly picked himself 
up, grimacing from the pain in his leg. But it wouldn't hold him. He 
collapsed to his knee and continued to stare. His chest was rising and 
falling quickly as his spark. His arms were shaking as well as he right 
foot. He mumbled nervously and in pain. The studied Megatron the hardest.

He watched as Megatron left and Pheniox and Marine was left. He glared at 
them, still ready to fire if they pulled something on him. He still didn't 
trust them. He thought it was nothing but a trick.
